{"tid":616086,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】美公布對華徵關稅清單 總值500億美元","createTime":"2018-04-04T01:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T01:29:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a9d4b1ee1acf228d7a7d9a8307984f6e54ee52","tid":616086,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T01:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180404/large/1522802562_6308.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180404%2Flarge%2F1522802562_6308.jpg&h=b1ce823e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表辦公室USTR公布針對中國進口商品徵關稅清單，總值約500億美元，大部份為高科技產品。<br />\n<br />\nUSTR表示，清單共1,300個關稅項目，商品對美國經濟負面影響輕微。今次有60日時間容許美國與中國就清單進行商討。<br />\n<br />\n中國商務部及外交部發聲明表示，美方不顧中方的嚴正交涉，亮無事實根據公布徵稅，是典型單邊主義和貿易保護主義，中方強烈讉責，堅決反對。又指美方做法違反了世貿組織的基本原則和精神。中方會立即將這一種錯誤做法訴諸世貿組織爭端解決機制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180404/58031648\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180404%2F58031648&d=fMMf8xppSEyiJECW3yj3UpnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=5c081874\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180404%2F58031648&h=9ce8de18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180404/58031648</a>"}]}